50#ifndef READERWRITER_H_
51#define READERWRITER_H_
52
53#include "create.h"
54
55#include "memory.h"
56
57/* if this is defined, we'll use mmap in preference to file ops */
58#define USE_MMAP_FOR_FILES 1
59
60void pgp_reader_set_fd(pgp_stream_t *, int);
61void pgp_reader_set_mmap(pgp_stream_t *, int);
62void pgp_reader_set_memory(pgp_stream_t *, const void *, size_t);
63
64/* Do a sum mod 65536 of all bytes read (as needed for secret keys) */
65void pgp_reader_push_sum16(pgp_stream_t *);
66uint16_t pgp_reader_pop_sum16(pgp_stream_t *);
67
68void pgp_reader_push_se_ip_data(pgp_stream_t *, pgp_crypt_t *,
69 pgp_region_t *);
70void pgp_reader_pop_se_ip_data(pgp_stream_t *);
71
72/* */
73unsigned pgp_write_mdc(pgp_output_t *, const uint8_t *);
74unsigned pgp_write_se_ip_pktset(pgp_output_t *, const uint8_t *,
75 const unsigned,
76 pgp_crypt_t *);
77void pgp_push_enc_crypt(pgp_output_t *, pgp_crypt_t *);
78int pgp_push_enc_se_ip(pgp_output_t *, const pgp_key_t *, const char *);
79
80/* Secret Key checksum */
81void pgp_push_checksum_writer(pgp_output_t *, pgp_seckey_t *);
82unsigned pgp_pop_skey_checksum_writer(pgp_output_t *);
83
84
85/* memory writing */
86void pgp_setup_memory_write(pgp_output_t **, pgp_memory_t **, size_t);
87void pgp_teardown_memory_write(pgp_output_t *, pgp_memory_t *);
88
89/* memory reading */
90void pgp_setup_memory_read(pgp_io_t *,
91 pgp_stream_t **,
92 pgp_memory_t *,
93 void *,
94 pgp_cb_ret_t callback(const pgp_packet_t *,
95 pgp_cbdata_t *),
96 unsigned);
97void pgp_teardown_memory_read(pgp_stream_t *, pgp_memory_t *);
98
99/* file writing */
100int pgp_setup_file_write(pgp_output_t **, const char *, unsigned);
101void pgp_teardown_file_write(pgp_output_t *, int);
102
103/* file appending */
104int pgp_setup_file_append(pgp_output_t **, const char *);
105void pgp_teardown_file_append(pgp_output_t *, int);
106
107/* file reading */
108int pgp_setup_file_read(pgp_io_t *,
109 pgp_stream_t **,
110 const char *,
111 void *,
112 pgp_cb_ret_t callback(const pgp_packet_t *,
113 pgp_cbdata_t *),
114 unsigned);
115void pgp_teardown_file_read(pgp_stream_t *, int);
116
117unsigned pgp_reader_set_accumulate(pgp_stream_t *, unsigned);
118
119/* useful callbacks */
120pgp_cb_ret_t pgp_litdata_cb(const pgp_packet_t *, pgp_cbdata_t *);
121pgp_cb_ret_t pgp_pk_sesskey_cb(const pgp_packet_t *, pgp_cbdata_t *);
122pgp_cb_ret_t pgp_get_seckey_cb(const pgp_packet_t *, pgp_cbdata_t *);
123
124int pgp_getpassphrase(void *, char *, size_t);
125
126#endif /* READERWRITER_H_ */
